#
# Implementing M-N-K-game in ATS2
#

######
#
# Part1-2
#
######

I present in this part an implementation of M-N-K-game in a style of
sequential programming. Basically, any input from a player comes from
the standard input channel (STDIN).

To compile, please just do 'make'. Then an excutable 'mygame' is generated.
Please do './mygame' to execute it.

###### end of [README] ######
